User satisfaction is a fundamental aspect of system evaluation and embraces user information satisfaction that emphasizes information requirements [17]. Because of the critical importance of information support in an IDI system, we explicitly focused on user information satisfaction and tested the following hypothesis. \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
